          <name>FLASH_EX_OP_REGION_UNLOCK</name>
          <briefdescription>
<para>Unlocks all regions of flash memory. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>This operation iterates over all lock regions of the main flash array and issues an Unlock Region (UR) command for each one.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
